## System Components & Architecture

- **Servo Motors (Ãƒâ€”5):** Provide bending and waveform locomotion along the spine.
- **Arduino Uno:** Drives PWM outputs, reads sensors, and orchestrates the control loop.
- **HC-SR04:** Mounted at the head for obstacle awareness.
